---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Studio — Narrative Attraction Agency for Higher Education"
  description="701am Studio — narrative attraction agency for higher education. Earned media, AI visibility, and social & new media campaigns. $6,500 per engagement, up to 50 placements.">
<div class="ph">
  <p class="ey">701am / Studio</p>
  <h1>The narrative attraction agency <span class="g">higher education trusts</span>.</h1>
  <p>We put your institution's story in the media, in AI search results, and in the feeds your future students actually scroll. <strong>Up to 50 placements per engagement. No long-term retainer.</strong></p>
  <div style="display:flex;gap:14px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:28px">
    <a href="/#contact" class="btn btn-p">Book a discovery call</a>
    <a href="/#hp-price" class="btn btn-o">$500 intro session</a>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="sec sec-c">
  <div class="w">
    <p style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;justify-content:center;font-size:14px;color:var(--txm);background:rgba(255,255,255,.6);border:1px solid var(--bl);border-radius:14px;padding:14px 20px;max-width:700px;margin:-40px auto 0">
      <span style="color:var(--co);font-weight:700">✓</span>
      <strong>Earned media only.</strong> We don't place sponsored content without labeling it. Every placement we earn is real coverage.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="sec sec-c" id="services">
  <div class="w">
    <div class="sh"><h2>What we <span class="g">do</span></h2><p>From earned media through AI visibility and social — every campaign managed across every channel that influences enrollment.</p></div>
    <div class="g3">
      <div class="cd">
        <p style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.06em;color:var(--co);margin-bottom:14px">Earned Media</p>
        <h3>Earned Media Campaigns</h3>
        <p>Full-cycle earned media — from data-story research through journalist outreach, placement tracking, and funnel correlation. Get covered in the publications your applicants actually read.</p>
        <ul style="margin-top:18px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px">
          <li style="font-size:13px;color:var(--txm);display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:8px"><span style="color:var(--co);font-weight:700">✓</span>Data-story research & narrative development</li>
          <li style="font-size:13px;color:var(--txm);display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:8px"><span style="color:var(--co);font-weight:700">✓</span>Journalist outreach & pitch writing</li>
          <li style="font-size:13px;color:var(--txm);display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:8px"><span style="color:var(--co);font-weight:700">✓</span>Placement tracking & coverage reporting</li>
        </ul>
        <p style="margin-top:20px;padding-top:16px;border-top:1px solid var(--bl);font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--txm)">$6,500 / engagement · up to 50 placements</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cd">
        <p style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.06em;color:var(--co);margin-bottom:14px">AI Visibility</p>
        <h3>AI Search Visibility</h3>
        <p>When students ask ChatGPT, Perplexity, or Google AI which program is best, your institution needs to be in the answer. We earn the citations and authority that train AI to recommend you.</p>
        <ul style="margin-top:18px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px">
          <li style="font-size:13px;color:var(--txm);display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:8px"><span style="color:var(--co);font-weight:700">✓</span>AI citation audit & competitive analysis</li>
          <li style="font-size:13px;color:var(--txm);display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:8px"><span style="color:var(--co);font-weight:700">✓</span>Signals strategy — what to earn and where</li>
          <li style="font-size:13px;color:var(--txm);display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:8px"><span style="color:var(--co);font-weight:700">✓</span>Quarterly AI visibility reporting</li>
        </ul>
        <p style="margin-top:20px;padding-top:16px;border-top:1px solid var(--bl);font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--txm)">$6,500 / engagement · up to 50 placements</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cd">
        <p style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.06em;color:var(--co);margin-bottom:14px">Social & New Media</p>
        <h3>Social &amp; New Media Campaigns</h3>
        <p>Your prospective students aren't reading press releases — they're on TikTok, Instagram, YouTube, and Reddit. We create platform-native content that meets them where they discover and decide.</p>
        <ul style="margin-top:18px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px">
          <li style="font-size:13px;color:var(--txm);display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:8px"><span style="color:var(--co);font-weight:700">✓</span>Platform-native content strategy & creation</li>
          <li style="font-size:13px;color:var(--txm);display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:8px"><span style="color:var(--co);font-weight:700">✓</span>Influencer & creator partnerships</li>
          <li style="font-size:13px;color:var(--txm);display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:8px"><span style="color:var(--co);font-weight:700">✓</span>Cross-platform performance tracking</li>
        </ul>
        <p style="margin-top:20px;padding-top:16px;border-top:1px solid var(--bl);font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--txm)">$6,500 / engagement · up to 50 placements</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="sec sec-d">
  <div class="w" style="position:relative;z-index:2">
    <div class="sh"><h2>Our <span class="g">process</span></h2><p>From story to student — every engagement follows a proven four-step methodology.</p></div>
    <div class="g3" style="grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr)">
      <div class="cd" style="background:var(--dkc);border-color:var(--dkb);color:var(--txd)">
        <p style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.06em;color:var(--am);margin-bottom:14px">01</p>
        <h3 style="color:#fff">Audit</h3>
        <p style="color:var(--txdm)">Review your institutional data, identify the stories hiding in plain sight, and assess your current visibility across press, AI, and social channels.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cd" style="background:var(--dkc);border-color:var(--dkb);color:var(--txd)">
        <p style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.06em;color:var(--am);margin-bottom:14px">02</p>
        <h3 style="color:#fff">Develop</h3>
        <p style="color:var(--txdm)">Frame the narrative, write the pitches, build the reporter list, and create platform-specific content for earned media, AI seeding, and social distribution.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cd" style="background:var(--dkc);border-color:var(--dkb);color:var(--txd)">
        <p style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.06em;color:var(--am);margin-bottom:14px">03</p>
        <h3 style="color:#fff">Place</h3>
        <p style="color:var(--txdm)">Human outreach to journalists, AI training data seeding, and social amplification. No mass emails. We work relationships, not databases.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cd" style="background:var(--dkc);border-color:var(--dkb);color:var(--txd)">
        <p style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.06em;color:var(--am);margin-bottom:14px">04</p>
        <h3 style="color:#fff">Report</h3>
        <p style="color:var(--txdm)">Every placement tracked and correlated to enrollment metrics, search visibility, and AI citation share. You'll know exactly what moved the needle.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="sec sec-c">
  <div class="w">
    <div class="sh"><h2>Not a traditional agency. <span class="g">Built for this.</span></h2><p>We've spent two decades in education visibility — not as spectators, but as the people who built the properties millions of prospective students used to compare programs.</p></div>
    <div class="g3">
      <div class="cd">
        <div class="ic">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><rect x="3" y="5" width="14" height="12" rx="2"/><path d="M7 5V3h6v2"/><path d="M7 10h6"/><path d="M7 13h3"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Higher ed is all we do</h3>
        <p>We don't serve every industry. Depth beats breadth — and we've spent 20 years on this exact corner of the media landscape.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cd">
        <div class="ic">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><circle cx="10" cy="10" r="8"/><circle cx="10" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Multi-channel by default</h3>
        <p>One placement works across press, AI, and social. We optimize for journalists, AI training signals, and the feeds where students spend their time.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cd">
        <div class="ic">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="M3 17l4-5 4 4 6-7"/><path d="M17 9V4h-5"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Data first</h3>
        <p>Every campaign starts with data — outcomes, enrollment patterns, regional comparisons. The best stories are already in your institutional data.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="sec sec-c" id="hp-price">
  <div class="w">
    <div class="sh"><h2>Simple pricing. <span class="g">No retainers.</span></h2><p>Every engagement scoped to deliver a specific number of placements. Start with a $500 session.</p></div>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:28px;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto">
      <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,.7);border:1px solid var(--bl);border-radius:24px;padding:36px 32px">
        <p style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em;color:var(--txm);margin-bottom:18px">Narrative Attraction Session</p>
        <div style="font-family:var(--serif);font-size:52px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.03em;line-height:1;color:var(--tx);margin-bottom:4px">$500</div>
        <p style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;color:var(--txm);margin-bottom:22px">one-time</p>
        <p style="font-size:14.5px;color:var(--txm);line-height:1.65;margin-bottom:28px">90 minutes with our team. Strategy session, data audit, channel plan.</p>
        <ul style="list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0 0 30px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px">
          <li style="font-size:15px;color:var(--tx);display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px"><span style="color:#2F9468;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0">✓</span>90-minute strategy session</li>
          <li style="font-size:15px;color:var(--tx);display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px"><span style="color:#2F9468;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0">✓</span>Data audit — find the stories</li>
          <li style="font-size:15px;color:var(--tx);display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px"><span style="color:#2F9468;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0">✓</span>Channel plan — press, AI, social</li>
          <li style="font-size:15px;color:var(--tx);display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px"><span style="color:#2F9468;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0">✓</span>No obligation to continue</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/#contact" class="btn btn-o" style="width:100%;justify-content:center">Book your session</a>
      </div>
      <div style="background:var(--dk);border:1px solid var(--dkb);border-radius:24px;padding:36px 32px;color:#fff">
        <p style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em;color:var(--txdm);margin-bottom:18px">Narrative Attraction Engagement</p>
        <div style="font-family:var(--serif);font-size:52px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.03em;line-height:1;margin-bottom:4px"><span class="g">$6,500</span></div>
        <p style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;color:var(--txdm);margin-bottom:22px">per engagement</p>
        <p style="font-size:14.5px;color:var(--txdm);line-height:1.65;margin-bottom:28px">Full campaign — research, narrative development, multi-channel outreach, and reporting. Up to 50 placements.</p>
        <ul style="list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0 0 30px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px">
          <li style="font-size:15px;color:var(--txd);display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px"><span style="color:#EE6A4C;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0">✓</span>All services included</li>
          <li style="font-size:15px;color:var(--txd);display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px"><span style="color:#EE6A4C;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0">✓</span>Up to 50 placements</li>
          <li style="font-size:15px;color:var(--txd);display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px"><span style="color:#EE6A4C;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0">✓</span>AI citation tracking</li>
          <li style="font-size:15px;color:var(--txd);display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px"><span style="color:#EE6A4C;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0">✓</span>Monthly reporting + review</li>
          <li style="font-size:15px;color:var(--txd);display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px"><span style="color:#EE6A4C;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0">✓</span>No long-term contract</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/#contact" class="btn btn-p" style="width:100%;justify-content:center">Book discovery call</a>
        <p style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--txdm);text-align:center;margin-top:16px">Most engagements finish in 8–12 weeks</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
